<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个叶子的茎在水下。”鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会把它咬断。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>叶子漂起来以后你就可以逃走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鱼儿们都潜到水下，开始咬叶子的茎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘听到蟾蜍回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人可以骂我的儿子！”蟾蜍太太大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快过来，克罗克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来了，妈妈。”克罗克在她后面大声回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点。”拇指姑娘对鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟾蜍走近了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，睡莲叶子开始漂动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看！”蟾蜍太太喊道，“她要逃走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快回来！”克罗克对拇指姑娘大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须得想个办法。”鱼儿们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然克罗克开始咯咯直笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快住手！”他大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鱼儿们围着两只蟾蜍，开始用他们的鱼鳍挠蟾蜍的痒痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走开。”贝尔普夫人大笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是鱼儿们没有停止。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘的睡莲叶子顺着小溪漂走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们，我的鱼儿朋友们。”拇指姑娘大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡莲叶子漂得越来越快，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘愉快地欣赏着周围的风景。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我终于获得自由了！”拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“树木和花朵多么美丽啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，拇指姑娘的睡莲叶子停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了，我被卡在石头上了。”她大声说，“我该怎么办呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只鸟开始唱歌，拇指姑娘往上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我有那只鸟的翅膀，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样我就能从这个睡莲叶子上飞走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只鸟有着亮蓝色的羽毛和美妙的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这里做什么？”鸟儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说来话长。总之，我被困住了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来帮助你。”鸟儿说，“你要去哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘停了一下，回答说，“去看看这个世界！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是皮特。”鸟儿说，“我可以和你一起去吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是拇指姑娘。”她高兴地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能和我一起去当然很好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特想办法帮助拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，他带着一根长长的绳子回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把这个系在睡莲叶子上面。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘照着做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后把另一边系在我的腿上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在呢？”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓紧了，拇指姑娘！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皮特飞了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡莲叶子变成了一条飞毯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它带着拇指姑娘飞在了水面之上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皮特，我在飞！”她大声说，“真好玩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风吹着拇指姑娘的头发，她开心地笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看着水里的鱼儿们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们对拇指姑娘摇着鱼鳞说再见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去看世界了！”拇指姑娘的新朋友大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风吹在她的脸颊上，她感到非常凉爽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得好自由。”她大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然有一个东西抓住了拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>